  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 13-65 years

          -  Received Autologous or Allogeneic hematopoietic stem cell transplantation.

          -  ECOG score 0-1.

          -  ICF is available.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Allergic to any therapy drug.

          -  Documented infection before neutropenia.

          -  Renal dysfunction.

          -  Suffering from central nervous system or mental disease.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
